{"tid":1880516,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西：中共利用華爲5G進行陰險侵略","createTime":"2020-02-15T01:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T11:00:56.000Z","uid":141151,"like":73,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6ece656e9e87facb090d4e85ae08d82cadebec81","tid":1880516,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"佩洛西：中共利用華爲5G進行陰險侵略<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ntdtv.com/b5/2020/02/14/a102777333.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2020%2F02%2F14%2Fa102777333.html&d=%2BKcr5gC3v3d6Nt4twTTWNj44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=3ab61550\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ntdtv.com/b5/2020/02/14/a102777333.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2020年02月15日訊】在週五開幕的慕尼黑安全會議上，美國衆院議長佩洛西警告歐洲盟國，警惕中共利用華爲5G技術進行陰險的侵略，不要選擇與華爲合作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國衆院議長佩洛西：「這是最陰險的侵略形式，使用由不認同我們價值觀的專制政權主導的5G通信方式。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n佩洛西警告歐洲盟國，用華爲產品來構建5G網絡，將會帶來嚴重的國家安全風險。<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\">美國衆院議長佩洛西：「我已經在貿易和其它領域盯着中共30多年了，在知識產權和其它方面，我可以毫不猶豫的告訴大家：如果你要選擇（華爲）這條路，就要非常小心，除非你願意淪爲和中（共）國一樣的社會或有一個和中（共）國一樣非自由企業模式的經濟。」</span></em><br />\n<br />\n在當天的會議上，白宮國際電信政策特別代表表示，美國正在尋求與電信企業建立合作，開發可以取代華爲的技術和產品。佩洛西對此表達相同立場。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國衆院議長佩洛西：「如果你想要建立一個有集體良知的價值觀，尊重人權等等，就不要選擇華爲，而是讓我們國際化，共同構建信息自由的產品。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n就在一天前，美國司法部剛剛對華爲追加了多項新指控，包括華爲違反了美國的《反黑法案》，竊取了6家美國科技公司的商業機密，以及違反國際制裁、與受制裁國家進行交易等。"},{"pid":"493e3f67eb78cee249a213b45cbccff9144f55c9","tid":1880516,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T01:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9722c7778d62128b963206dac1e8387ddbefc326","tid":1880516,"uid":18001,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T01:47:06.000Z","msg":"某日落帝國: 照奶"},{"pid":"491b9f922d4068f1623aeb0f3297fb45a59976b0","tid":1880516,"uid":224066,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T01:56:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1OL4itr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1OL4itr.jpg&h=3a88bce5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c634b7379f02734ee30a384ff259232a1cc33d49","tid":1880516,"uid":9315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T01:58:38.000Z","msg":"除非你願意淪爲和中（共）國一樣的社會或有一個和中（共）國一樣非自由企業模式的經濟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個問題就係有D國家真係心甘情願  咁冇野好講"},{"pid":"04dee0325946dc5c877cdc882b339098f8d3f5a0","tid":1880516,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T02:01:00.000Z","msg":"歐盟及某日落帝國 : 繼續奶共<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54a7daf23174d002a4306402c36d96f6dbc628c","tid":1880516,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019167357a925335a40a7a79128d816f1bc1281e","tid":1880516,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共和黨民主黨都反對中共華為</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"63b463f60a56ada0f641f4a8cc203f7f8d6783ef","tid":1880516,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019167357a925335a40a7a79128d816f1bc1281e","tid":1880516,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T15:08:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">共和黨民